Alec Worcester https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alec_Worcester 0 Alec Worcester (1887–1952) was a British stage and silent film actor. He played the lead role opposite Alma Taylor in The Cloister and the Hearth and was the lead in fifty shorts. He was married to the actress Violet Hopson until their divorce in 1919.
